Chapter 1: Instant crush
>You are Anon
>It’s your day off so you decide to go to your favorite little restaurant
>You walk in and wave to the waiter, an old fox who knows what you like
>You look around calmly and enjoy the atmosphere
>But... Somethings wrong
>You see a maned wolf, Raquel, another regular there
>Your table is to her right
>She's usually quite happy, and has a laugh that you swear fills the room
>To be honest you had a sort of crush on her but never had the balls to do anything about it
>But now she’s quietly sobbing, her ears drooped
>An uneaten steak on a plate in front of her
>A young man is sitting across from her
>You don't hear the whole conversation but he looks quite unhappy 
>"One of you people"
>"Cripple"
>"Worst date ever"
>You can see tears falling freely onto the steak
>With each word her ears droop a little bit more
>You aren't exactly one to get into other people’s business, but seeing this made you angry and upset
>You stand and walk over to them both
>You put a hand on the man’s shoulder
>"I think you should leave" you say firmly
>"What? Man mind your own fucking business" he says looking up at you
>You don't remove your hand 
>"It’s my business when I see someone making a lady cry" you say frowning
>"Now get out of here" 
