>"Sorry, I just couldn’t sit back and see that"
>Her ears are still drooped but she’s looking up at you with surprise in her eyes
>"I hope he didn’t ruin your meal and hope you don’t mind I stepped in" 
>"Oh. Oh no it’s fine...You're Anon right?" she says 
>So much sadness in her voice...
>"Mind if I join you? I would hate to leave a sad lady alone" you ask politely
>Her ears perk up a little
>"Oh uh...sure I would like that actually" she says with a faint smile
>You look at her and notice something that should have been painfully obvious
>Her left arm is gone just below the shoulder, the long sweater she was wearing tied in a knot at the end
>You don’t want to stare so instead you focus on the rest of her
>Her entire build is what you would call lanky
>Long legs, long arms...arm, and long neck
>Long fluffy tail that is swishing behind her with a tip of white fur
>Her fur is a golden brown,, a black streak running from between her ears down past where you could see
