>Her ears twirl and flick gently, the left one pierced towards the middle with a single gold ring
>You sit and smile at her, you get a small smile
>You wave to the waiter who is bringing you your usual meal of a bacon cheeseburger and fries
>"Ah here you are Anon, do enjoy" he says as he drops it off
