>Raquel is making a small fire pit, gathering stones to form a circle
>You go to gather the logs around and set a fire up
>Raquel watches as you walk around grabbing logs
>"You’re such a weird guy Anon" she says after you throw a termite infested log down the mountain
>You perk up and look at her
>"Yes, yes I am....but why am I this time?" you say as you dump the good logs you found into a pile and set up the campers stove on a boulder
>"You’re dating an Amputee maned wolf, take pleasure in stupid things like throwing rocks at the moon and yelling "fuck off space egg" and you drink and only get more romantic towards me" she says with her ears perked up and her tail swishing
