>"I don’t think I could be happier than I am with you now" she says softly "with or without my arm"
>You turn and pull her into a close hug
>"I’m glad you’re happy again, you deserve that"

>Dusk flows into night
>Raquel tells you about her childhood, her parents who live in Brazil, How she was raised in the US by her aunt, how her aunt died a few years ago in a car accident
