>She’s quiet for a moment
>"You never asked how I lost my arm" she says drinking the final few drops and setting the flask down
>You look to her
>The firelight dances in her eyes, her golden brown fur shimmering 
>"I figured you would tell me when you were ready" 
>"It was... stupid" she says 
